posting_body: ['Erlands Point Apartments', '3000 Austin DR, Bremerton, WA, 98312', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 2', 'OR Text', '2', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our leasing team.', 'Use this link for more information:', '<URL>', 'Did you take a close look at this fantastic floorplan?', ' It actually has two, huge, lighted walk-in closets in the bedroom!!', " Imagine all the fun you'll have filling them up!!", ' The bathroom even has two sinks in it!!', " This end unit is styled with vaulted ceilings and new carpet, this is the home you've been waiting for!!", "Available to prelease today, we're only a phone call away!!", 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 700 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Experience the benefit of a private community with the convenience of a fantastic location!', 'Nestled in a quiet wooded setting with fine dining, superb shopping and the Seattle ferry only minutes away.', 'Easy highway access makes your commute a dream come true!', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet friendly (no weight restrictions)', 'Breed restrictions', 'Income Requirements:', 'Two and a half monthly rent', 'Driving Directions:', 'From highway 3, exit Austin Drive and turn right ) from southbound hwy 3, exit Austin Drive and turn left over freeway).', 'Erlands Point Apartments will be on the right with a shared entrance with the Naval Hospital.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:8:30AM-5:30PM', '1pOwBhXshV']
